[Agent Cutscene 1]: 
	After Jen and tipzl flee the apartment and inspect the corpse of aphie and flee down
  an alleyway and set out to look for hatman, the police will break down their apartment door and the 
  agents will emerge from them and inspect the room, finding the doomer pamphlets hatman gave to the pair
  with their final estrogen delivery. Agent 1 will show Agent 2 and in the background the Agent 3 will look 
  out the window.

  Throughout act one the agents will be following Jen and Tipzl acting as a specific threat they're unaware of.

	What the players should be wondering is how the agents or general police forces knew that meta humans 
  lived in apartment 41 and how much they know  about their targets. While the players will encounter random 
  police forces throughout the game the agents are a seemingly unstoppable force specifically tracking them 
  through the world. The agent's perspective of following the player characters will also contrast the things the 
  characters are doing and their decisions.

